:{{DIcon|Talk}} Herta Department of Implement Arts?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010616-->
::'''Wen Mingde:''' Ha! An important department within the space station, Implement Arts is. We oversee the incoming and outgoing of all our assets, including inventory checks and counts.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' Furthermore, we maintain close communications with Interastral Peace Corporation. For someone as well-traveled as yourself, I'm sure you've heard of our reputation.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Curio Collection Squad?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010619-->
::'''Wen Mingde:''' The Curio Collection Squad is a temporary emergency unit established by the space station to address the needs of the post-disaster revival.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' As the name suggests, it is mainly responsible for collecting the Curios that have been displaced due to the recent monster invasion.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Safe zone?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010622-->
::'''Wen Mingde:''' It is the very ground on which we stand. The stronghold from which the space station researchers fought back against the Antimatter Legion.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' Although the situation is generally under control, the monsters have not been completely wiped out.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' The safe zone is the result of our transition plan, for us to take back all the lost zones. I am confident all the dots will eventually be connected.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have any other questions.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010626-->
::'''Wen Mingde:''' Good. For any questions you may encounter in the future, my young friend, please do not hesitate to come to me.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' In the future, there is much I must rely on you for.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
