::'''Wen Mingde:''' Please allow me to introduce myself again. I am Wen Mingde, head of the Herta Department of Implement Arts. I am also the Curio Collection Squad Leader, in charge of establishing safe areas in the base zone.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' Allow me to be frank. I am currently troubled by the lack of human resources available for the Curio Collection Squad.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' There are four zones in the space station. With our current capacity, we can only take care of one. If the situation persists, I wonder when we will achieve the objective we have set out in the Declaration of Revival.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' After calming myself down and giving it some thought, I realized that recruiting external members may be the solution.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' While I was lingering on that thought, you began a conversation with me. What a pleasant coincidence.
::'''Wen Mingde:''' If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to let me know.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_500010109_370-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_500010109_370-->
